### Roles API - Nexus AAAIMX

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

@targetUserId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003
@newRoleId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003
@divisionId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002
@clubId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003
@roleId = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174003

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Get Roles Catalog
# Description: Retrieves all roles in the system catalog (requires authentication).
# Note: Only users with roles other than "member" or "senior member" can access this endpoint.
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Get Assignable Roles (roles that current user can assign)
# Description: Get roles that the current user can assign to others based on their permissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/assignable

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Get Users with Roles (for management interface)
# Description: Get users with their roles for role management interface
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/users

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Get Users with Roles - Filtered by Division
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/users?divisionId={{divisionId}}

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Get Users with Roles - Filtered by Club
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/users?clubId={{clubId}}

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Get Users with Roles - Filtered by Role
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/users?roleId={{roleId}}

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Get Users with Roles - Paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles/users?skip=0&limit=20

# ------------------------------------------------------------
### Assign Role to User
# Description: Assign a role to a user (requires role management permissions)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/roles/assign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "{{targetUserId}}",
  "newRoleId": "{{newRoleId}}"
}